# Core invariants

Replace the placeholders below with **3–5** rules that caused real incidents when violated. The evolution system can add more over time via `.claude/memory/learned-rules.md`.

1. **[Your most painful bug pattern]** — Describe what must never happen and the correct pattern.
2. **[Second critical failure mode]** — Same.
3. **[Safety / data-loss rule]** — Something that must always hold.

Until customized, default to **AGENTS.md** forbidden patterns and verification gates.
